original_title: Blue Öyster Cult: Some Other Enchanted Evening
overview: Some Other Enchanted Evening was released for the first in 2007 by Legacy Records as part of the reissue set for the SOME ENCHANTED EVENING live album.  Recorded 1978 direct to 3/4 inch video at The Capitol Center, Largo, MD on July 14, 1978.  Previously Unreleased Live Recording.  Set List: Set List: R.U. Ready 2 Rock, E.T.I., Harvester of Eyes, We Gotta Get Out of This Place, Golden Age of Leather, Astronomy, ME 262, Kick Out the James, This Ain't The Summer of Love, 5 Guitars, Born to Be Wild.
title: Blue Öyster Cult: Some Other Enchanted Evening
